headline: Bruker, Agilent, Revvity, Avantor, and Bio-Techne Shares Are Soaring, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks jumped in the afternoon session after reports revealed a potential drug-pricing agreement between the White House and the pharmaceutical industry.
